      "raw_text": "The farmers union, which is\nknown as the American Society OF\nEquity, was allowed partial affilia\nton with the American Federation\nof Labor yesterday. The fedora.\nton will aid the farmers in sell.\ning union label farm and orchard\nproducts, the object being to cut\nthe middle men. 1t was claimed\nthat the commission or middle\nmen placed the price on farm pro\nduce for both producer and con-\nsumner, and one of the primary OBJ.\njects of the alliance will be to do\naway with the speculator, who\nneither sows nor spins. Commit,\ntees were named to formulate a\nunion label arrangement for the\nunion label in farm business."
